Usually seeds, eggs and neonates are not delivered continuously but released in discrete batches, i.e., sowings, clutches and litters. The total offspring mass (mr) accumulated in a period between two successive reproductive events (τr) equals: 3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
